n and profit tax by over  billion rmb yuan it contributed excellently to the china’s electronic information industry         irico group corporation was formerly named shaanxi irico color picture tube plant coded  and was established in the s it was a stateowned sole proprietorship enterprise established under the concert and approval of the leaders of central cpc committee and the state council for the china’s color tvs industry after the development and grandness of over  years irico group has already grown up to the influential group in electronic information enterprise it has  second level solely funded and holding subcompanies and  joint stock companies it also has two listed companies irico stock sh and irico electronics hk  the company now has total assets of near  billion rmb yuan and near  employees         for over the past three decades after overcoming countless of difficulties and frustrations irico people has always been holding the strong willpower and industriously perfecting its business they based upon the domestic market and gestated many no in the electronic information industry in china irico is the birthplace of the first cpt and the first set of cpt glass bulb in china it is a cpt production company with the greatest production capacity and most powerful assorting capacity in china which has also sent a colorful world for over  million of families in total irico is the birthplace of the first projection tube in china its selfdeveloped projection tube with big screen high brightness and high definition once ranked the famous branded product in the same business in the world irico is the birthplace of the first piece of pdp display device in china it’s the unique pdp middle testing line in china once made tremendous contribution to the development of the new display devices in china irico is the birthplace of the first piece of oled display device in china since its starting investment and attempts in  it has made the breakthrough for the development of oled business in china irico is also the birthplace of the first tftlcd glass substrate in china its selfowned intellectual property in glass substrate added up the vancancy in china smashed the technical blockade from the foreign countries for many years and rewrote the history of the disability for china to produce tftlcd glass substrate irico will soon make the new breakthrough in above gen lcd glass substrate and the gen tvuse display devices amoled which shall make new contributions to the display devices industry in china          irico group has been sticking the development trace characterized by “make the corporate more stronger with the help of technology” while it constantly upgrades the business scale and managerial level she stood besides the profound cultural accumulation and resource advantages has already established the enterprise technical centre of statelevel patent workstation and post doctor workstation moreover the company has been honored with many rewards like the national scientific  technological advance prize top leading informationized enterprises in china it has been awarded with the honorary titles of “national innovative enterprise” “national enterprises and government units intellectual property demonstration company” currently the business of cpt lcd glass and illumination materials etc in irico occupies the leading position in the world and the business of green lighting led chips oled pv glass etc ranks the leading position in the domestic market         for many years the party central committee and the state council have always been concerning and supporting the development of irico the leaders of the cpc and the country visited the irico to inspect and direct the work successively such as hu jintao jiang zemin wu bangguo wen jiabao and zhang dejiang etc they also gave the fully recognition and highly appraisal for the development of irico          since the negative affects brought by the shock of the financial crisis and the upgrading of the industry in the past couple of years under the leadership of the general manager xing daoqin and the leading group all the irico people have been insisting the guidance of scientific development outlook jointing everyone’s hands to work together to conquer the current difficulties with strong willpower and sparing no efforts to propel the strategic transformation of the company the company has successfully accomplished the new stride from “to make the cpts stronger and innovate the business” to “make restructuring to optimization strive for strongness in a steady and quick way” which has been coming into form of the strategic pattern featured by the three major business clusters irico group corp and its listing subsidiaries——irico display devices co ltd and irico group electronics co ltd which lay special emphasis on developing the photoelectron related businessspecifically develops the led epiwafer  chip led encapsulation led illumination led display panel led backlight and new energy resources etc display devices businessspecially develops the newly display devices like lcd oled pdp fed etc and cpt and components materials business specially develops electronic glass products illumination materials and metal components etc respectively the company has basically accomplished the development transformation from the simplification in business to that in diversification some further enhancement has been made in the aspects of company vitality controlling force and influence          looking forward to the future irico people has full confidence and enthusiasm they are ready to abide the managerial concept of “creator of the happy life for mankind” and strictly conform to the corporate spirit of “for people for business in pursuit of excellent” the company shall be based upon the chief business positioning and determine to make the irico group corp to be the most fast growing company in the photoelectron field of the electronic information industry in china irico is fully prepared to make much more contributions to accomplishing the targets of the construction of an innovative nation and a harmonious society   copyright   chcomcn　all right reserved address： norainbow road xianyang cityshaanxi province  china  tel： zip： hk company profile  executives  irico group new energy co ltd  wall street journal dow jones a news corp company news corp is a network of leading companies in the worlds of diversified media news education and information services dow jones barrons bigcharts djx dow jones newswires factiva financial news mansion global marketwatch newsmart newsplus private markets risk  compliance wsjcom wsj pro wsj conference wsj video news corp big decisions business spectator checkout harper collins new york post proptiger rea realtorcom storyful the australian the sun the times djia ▲     sp  ▲     nasdaq ▲     us  yr ▲  yield    crude oil ▲     euro ▲     subscribe now sign in the wall street journal asia edition us asia europe india  china  japan  august  todays paper sections my journal home world us politics economy business tech markets opinion arts life real estate todays paper show all sections hide all sections world home africa asia canada china europe latin america middle east economy world video us home economy law new york politics real time economics washington wire journal report us video whats news podcast politics home washington wire politics video wsjnbc news poll economy home real time economics economic forecasting survey economy video business home management techwsjd aerospace  defense autos  transportation commercial real estate consumer products energy entrepreneurship financial services food  services health care hospitality law manufacturing media  marketing natural resources retail cfo journal cio journal cmo today logistics report risk  compliance heard on the street business video journal report business podcast tech home cio journal geoffrey fowler christopher mims joanna s